  "detailed_description": "Control various machinery through keyboard or mouse clicks, change the direction of garbage delivery, and transport the garbage to the garbage station.<br>When the garbage station collects enough garbage, you can press the space on the keyboard to clear the level.<br>You can also challenge to collect stars and sea lions, and then clear the level after completing all the collections.<br><br>Type of machinery<br>·obstacle<br>Change the direction of garbage movement by rotation/displacement.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/777f329703422e52f79b03d85ae629d9.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/777f329703422e52f79b03d85ae629d9.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/777f329703422e52f79b03d85ae629d9.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·conveyor belt<br>When activated, it can push garbage in one direction.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/ef64a2320f9a23c775fc79f2aa702938.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/ef64a2320f9a23c775fc79f2aa702938.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/ef64a2320f9a23c775fc79f2aa702938.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·sensor<br>Activates when it touches garbage or certain objects, starting the associated machinery. Turns off when there is no contact.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/4c9678b67ac1d8b7b3f81cf515c4bb4b.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/4c9678b67ac1d8b7b3f81cf515c4bb4b.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/4c9678b67ac1d8b7b3f81cf515c4bb4b.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·Transport box<br>Two as a group, can be switched to input/output state.<br>Only when one is the input port and the other is the output port will it work, transporting the garbage from the input port to the output port.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/03a1273f50f9d36d550fc92178a7982b.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/03a1273f50f9d36d550fc92178a7982b.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/03a1273f50f9d36d550fc92178a7982b.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·magnet<br>It can absorb and push away the surrounding garbage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/7a09ff07b4b21abde1b2de0674e18410.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/7a09ff07b4b21abde1b2de0674e18410.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/7a09ff07b4b21abde1b2de0674e18410.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>·Glide track<br>Drive other machinery to move.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/45e3509e7161c73ec2710f282978ca57.poster.avif?t=1653037555\" width=200 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/45e3509e7161c73ec2710f282978ca57.webm?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1979480/extras/45e3509e7161c73ec2710f282978ca57.mp4?t=1653037555\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
